        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          No hidden costs, no surprise fees. Clear pricing from the start with ongoing support 
          that fits your budget. Choose the perfect plan for your business needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

